QuestData.Title: Sticky Situation
QuestData.Description: We were hauling batteries to the excavation site and I crashed my freakin' car!$B$BMy sister didn't even look back. I took the turn a little fast, so what? It happens!$B$BPoint is, the batteries went flying everywhere and I'm in no condition to lift them out.$B$BSo what do you say? Wanna help me out?
QuestData.RewardText: You're a real doll. Let's get out of here.
